Package edu.uml.cs.isense.dfm

Class Summary
DataFieldManager The DataFieldManager class is designed to, as its name implies, manage how data is associated with project fields on the iSENSE website.
FieldMatching The FieldMatching class lists off fields from a project, which the implementor must pass in as an intent extra to DFM_ORDER_LIST, and makes a best attempt of matching them with known field names in the system.
Fields This is the class container for all recorded data.
